cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference skill-fuse in a blog post, talk, or paper, cite it as follows."
title: "skill-fuse: AI skill fusion for SKILL.md-based agents"
abstract: >-
  skill-fuse composes two AI agent skills (SKILL.md files) into a single fused
  skill that any Claude Code / Codex / Cursor / Windsurf / Gemini CLI session
  can invoke as a new /command. Zero-dependency: bash + markdown, no build
  step, no config.
type: software
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/gaia-research/skill-fuse"
url: "https://github.com/gaia-research/skill-fuse#readme"
keywords:
  - ai-skill-fusion
  - agent-skill-merge
  - skill-md-compose
  - claude-code
  - anthropic
  - agent-skills
  - developer-tools
  - open-source
authors:
